For more information please provide your contact information by texting "Home" to  <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/ral/apa/7504213509/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
<br>
<br>
We serve the Raleigh Metro Area's following city limits: Knightdale, Clayton, Garner, Raleigh.<br>
<br>
Welcome to Birkhead Realty Group affiliated with Fathom Realty.  We are licensed real estate brokers based in Clayton, NC.  Our primary goal is to help individuals and families sell or buy a home, but "life happens" and we understand that homeownership today isn't an option for everyone.  We encourage waiting until homeownership is an option, but sometimes renter-buyers can't wait.<br>
<br>
Contact us to learn more about an innovative Lease with Right to Purchase program. Unlike many rent to own programs or lease options, there is no obligation to buy and no non-refundable option fees.  Typically market available leases start at $1,900 per month and as high as $2,800 per month for homes valued between $320K and $500K.  Lease down payments begin at 2X the monthly rent; plus, pet deposit if applicable.<br>
<br>
Typical Requirements to Qualify:<br>
• Annual household income of $50,000+<br>
• Stable employment<br>
• No history of eviction or other landlord issues • No pending bankruptcy<br>
• No disqualifying criminal history<br>
<br>
Thank you in advance for trusting us with this important decision,<br>
David Birkhead (License# 317650)<br>
Like us on Facebook @birkheadrealty<br>
